{"tid":89862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普：美國優先！買美國貨、雇美國人","createTime":"2017-01-21T15:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T16:28:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1740e30082c7112e3942a3794c74057534c9891d","tid":89862,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:45:25.000Z","msg":"〔記者楊芙宜／台北報導〕川普宣誓為美國第45任總統後，發表就職演說時指出，美國人民齊聚在華府見證政權和平交接，從現在起，新政府治理觀念將是「美國優先」，他絕對不會讓人民失望，美國人將再次獲勝！<br />\n川普表示，政權交接是人民作主時刻，最重要的不是從一個政黨把權力轉移到另一個政黨，而是把權力交到人民手中。<br />\n他說，新政府將帶領美國人民重新拿回工作、邊界管理權、財富和美國夢；新政府將要蓋新道路、橋樑、機場...還有建設美國整個國家。<br />\n川普指出，新政府將帶領人民「買美國貨，雇美國人！」讓美國重返偉大。"},{"pid":"3628b2e8839ae7892d76296f38d0f6248edfeac9","tid":89862,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5315900b9ec072299888340914d3d268ccf319","tid":89862,"uid":10441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:53:46.000Z","msg":"抄我地689既港人優先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccacb5ee1bf409744cac2fb0ae7087ec2085885","tid":89862,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:55:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抄我地689既港人優先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國優先！用中國貨、僱中國人"},{"pid":"bb2aab42aa5cd2d786a03018abc6df6ac5a600a1","tid":89862,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"阿森一族真係預言卡通片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb76cdeebccd0371f7b32b6d3a5df50ab2ccad83","tid":89862,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:01:44.000Z","msg":"有預感支那經濟係Trump 帶領美國情況下會超越美國"},{"pid":"11a57ebb8e4f43090491f64472446b5c8e32b5fd","tid":89862,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:02:40.000Z","msg":"愛祖國 用國貨<img src=\"/